Package: vdr-plugin-pvrinput
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${vdr:Depends}
Description: VDR plugin allowing to use a Hauppauge PVR card as input device
 This plugin uses a Hauppauge PVR card as an input device. All cards
 supported by the ivtv driver should work.

